 He didnt make an expression of any kind. "I like you darkmouse. Your 
resourceful cunning and very smart. In that I know i cant force you to saty 
here so im giveing you a choice. I invite you to stay with us until you 
decided wiether or not you want to join us. Id rather have you as an allie or 
comrade then an enemy." He looked back at the hologram. All the bases on 
earth and the ark on the moon lit up.
